ActNorthwest Territories Act
SubjectNWT Supreme Court - Deputy Judge Arthur M. Gans
PrecisOrder appointing the Honourable ARTHUR M. GANS as a deputy judge of the SUPREME COURT of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES, to hold office during good behaviour until attaining the age of seventy-five years.
